The '''Militia Camp''' is a building in the [[Levy Barracks]] category. It is used to recruit [[Militia]].

== Production ==
The Militia Camp produces one [[Militia]] every 15 seconds. It consumes 12 [[Wheat]] and 15 [[Wood]] per cycle.

